Subject: Attention Journal

Description: Append-only event journal for recording attention movement and intention chains separately from narrative interpretation.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-28_attention_journal_system\Dictated_Attention_Journal_System_Source.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-28_attention_journal_continuity\Dictated_Attention_Journal_Continuity_Source.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\AttentionRuntimeRegistry.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SemanticCognitionOperatingLoop.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\TurnBookmark.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\TrailingChecksumVoice.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\attention_layers\NarrativeDigestion.sop
@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\SectionedPeripheryAssociationFabric.sop
